## Base Solution: Spring Boot API with Hardcoded Data (DTO-Based)

### **📌 Overview**
This solution implements a **proper DTO-based architecture** with hardcoded data before integrating Azure Cosmos DB.
✔ **Uses DTO (Data Transfer Object) to separate request/response from Entity.**  
✔ **Removes direct Entity exposure in API.**  
✔ **Introduces a Mapper class for conversion between Entity and DTO.**  
✔ **Ensures validation on input DTOs.**  

